            "text": " $$ \\begin{aligned} P_{(t,T)}^{(A)} &= \\frac{A_t + A_T}{2} \\big( \\chi_T - \\chi_t \\big) \\text{(= $P_{(t,T)}^{(A)}(\\chi)$)} \\\\ &\\quad + \\frac{\\chi_t + \\chi_T}{2} \\Bigg( \\frac{A_T(r_T,x_T) - A_T(r_t,x_T) + A_t(r_T,x_T) - A_t(r_t,x_T)}{2} \\Bigg) \\text{(=: $P_{(t,T)}^{(A)}(r)$)} \\\\ &\\quad + \\frac{\\chi_t + \\chi_T}{2} \\Bigg( \\frac{A_T(r_T,x_T) - A_T(r_T,x_t) + A_t(r_T,x_T) - A_t(r_T,x_t)}{2} \\Bigg) \\text{(=: $P_{(t,T)}^{(A)}(x)$)} \\\\ &\\quad + \\frac{\\chi_t + \\chi_T}{2} \\Bigg( \\frac{A_T(r_T,x_t) - A_T(r_t,x_T) + A_t(r_T,x_t) - A_t(r_t,x_T)}{2} \\Bigg). \\text{(=: $P_{(t,T)}^{(A)}(\\text{carry})$)} \\end{aligned} $$",
